subject: Sailboats and Sailing
America's Cup
lead_paragraph: The New York Supreme Court set a date of Feb. 25 to hear BMW Oracle’s complaint that Alinghi, the defending America’s Cup champion from Switzerland, breached Cup rules by having its sails made abroad.
